title: I: Revocation - A Runescape PK Video by Doodlepieguy
description:
This is the first Runescape PK Video by the Player Moderator Doodlepieguy, entitled Revocation. This file is .wmv. It is a little over 75kb, and 17 minutes. Originally seeded by its creator.

Doodle can be contacted on the forums of Runevillage.com, under the user name &#039;Doodle&#039;.

A special edition of this video with directors commentary is also available.

Enjoy.
